      "term": "president",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "B2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "the person who is the leader or head of a country, organization, or group, especially the head of state in a republic",
          "examples": [
            "The president outlined new policies in her speech.",
            "He was elected president of the student council."
